&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cfstats:&lt;br/&gt;
                Column Family: testcfsize&lt;br/&gt;
                SSTable count: 1&lt;br/&gt;
                Space used (live): 14395&lt;br/&gt;
                Space used (total): 5491&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13151127" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 16 Nov 2011 10:35:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch lgtm, +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13151387" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 16 Nov 2011 18:10:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Tried to catch the bug w/ a check on live size in RecoveryManagerTruncateTest, but I couldn&apos;t reproduce the race without adding sleeps inside the deletion task.  So I just committed the patch as above.)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
